bilingual.source: The siren of the ambulance is very loud.
He was taken to the hospital by ambulance.
bilingual.target: 他被救护车送到了医院。

bilingual.source: There is emergency equipment in the ambulance.
The ambulance rushed the patient to the hos.

bilingual.source: The sound of the ambulance siren filled the air.
bilingual.target: 救护车的警笛声充满了空气。

bilingual.source: The patient was transported to the hospital by ambulance.
bilingual.target: 病人被救护车送往医院。

bilingual.source: The traffic jam hindered the ambulance's passage.
bilingual.target: 交通堵塞妨碍了救护车的通行。

bilingual.source: The ambulance arrived at the accident scene quickly.
bilingual.target: 救护车很快就到了事故现场。

bilingual.source: The ambulance arrived at the scene within minutes.
bilingual.target: 救护车几分钟内就到达了现场。

list.abstract: ambulance（[ˈæmbjələns]），英语单词。作名词为救护车。作动词为用救护车送。例句：Soon an ambulance (救护车) arrived and took the boy to the hospital.（很快，一辆救护车到达，将男孩送到医院）。 近义词为meat wagon。
《Ambulance》是日本女子偶像组合AKB48的专辑《希望的リフレイン》里的单曲。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it seems we've reached an impasse. I could call you a cab or an ambulance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来我们到达了一个僵局，我可以帮你叫辆的士或者救护车。

yingyinNormal.en: OK, a fully equipped ambulance, Molly can examine me on the way, it'll save time. Ready to go, Molly?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，有了装备齐全的救护车，茉莉可以在路上给我做检查，省点时间。准备好了吗，茉莉 ？

yingyinNormal.en: Can we come too? Of course. Let's go. Are we going in an ambulance? No. The mountain's too far away. We'll go in my aeroplane. Aeroplane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔，我们可以跟你一起去吗？当然可以，我们走吧！我们是不是要坐救护车去？不是，山离这里有很远的的路程！我们要坐我的飞机过去！唔！飞机！唔！

yingyinNormal.en: A few months ago, I saw inspiration of a different kind when I opened the new Cambridge base of the East Anglian Air Ambulance, where Prince William works as a helicopter pilot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 数月以前，我看到了另一种不同形式的激励，当我开放"东盎格鲁空中救护车"(英国的一个直升机救护医疗机构)的剑桥站时，威廉王子作为一名飞行员在那工作。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a vehicle specially equipped for taking sick or injured people to and from the hospital, especially in emergencies

examination_example.sentence: Soon an <highlight>ambulance</highlight> (救护车) arrived and took the boy to the hospital.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很快，一辆救护车到达，将男孩送到医院。

examination_example.sentence: I’ll send an <highlight>ambulance</highlight> (救护车) as soon as possible.
